---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Monogate — One Operator for All Elementary Functions"
  description="16 operators. 14 nodes. 80.8% savings. Proved optimal."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Monogate monogram" class="logo" width="240" height="150" />
    <h1 class="tagline">
      One operator generates all elementary functions.<br />
      We found 16 and proved the optimal routing.
    </h1>
    <ul class="stats" aria-label="Key statistics">
      <li><span class="num">16</span><span class="lbl">operators</span></li>
      <li><span class="num">14</span><span class="lbl">nodes</span></li>
      <li><span class="num">80.8%</span><span class="lbl">savings</span></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <nav class="cards" aria-label="Key pages">
    <a class="card" href="/superbest">
      <span class="card-k">▣</span>
      <span class="card-t">SuperBEST</span>
      <span class="card-d">The optimal routing table — 10 operations at 14 EML nodes.</span>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="/proofs">
      <span class="card-k">✓</span>
      <span class="card-t">Proofs</span>
      <span class="card-d">50 Lean originals across 14 files. Zero sorries in 13 of 14 files. Verified by `lake build`, not peer-reviewed.</span>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="https://monogate.dev/lab">
      <span class="card-k">◈</span>
      <span class="card-t">Explorer</span>
      <span class="card-d">Interactive fractal + synthesis + symbolic regression tools.</span>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="/paper">
      <span class="card-k">∫</span>
      <span class="card-t">Paper</span>
      <span class="card-d">The full arXiv:2603.21852 treatment and theorem catalog.</span>
    </a>
  </nav>

  <p class="readmore">
    Read the full story →
    <a href="/one-operator"><strong>One Operator</strong></a>
  </p>

  <p class="footnote">
    <span style="color: var(--muted);">
      30 theorems · 265 equations costed · 50 Lean theorems ·
      <a href="https://pypi.org/project/monogate/"><code>pip install monogate</code></a> ·
      <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.21852">arXiv:2603.21852</a>
    </span>
  </p>

  <style>
    section.hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 72px 0 40px;
    }
    .logo {
      height: 150px;
      width: auto;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      display: block;
      /* logo.svg is white; no filter needed on dark bg */
    }
    .tagline {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.35;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      color: var(--text);
      max-width: 640px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    ul.stats {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 56px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      padding: 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    ul.stats li {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    ul.stats .num {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--orange);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    ul.stats .lbl {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    nav.cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 48px auto 32px;
    }
    nav.cards a.card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    nav.cards a.card:hover {
      border-color: var(--orange);
      background: var(--surface);
      text-decoration: none;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    nav.cards .card-k {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      color: var(--orange);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    nav.cards .card-t {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    nav.cards .card-d {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    p.readmore {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0 16px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    p.readmore a { color: var(--cyan); }

    p.footnote {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 2;
    }
    p.footnote code { background: var(--surface); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px; }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      section.hero { padding: 48px 0 28px; }
      .logo { height: 120px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
      .tagline { font-size: 1.4rem; }
      ul.stats { gap: 30px; }
      ul.stats .num { font-size: 1.5rem; }
      nav.cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-top: 36px; }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
